# Ludo Game Simulation

A Python-based simplified Ludo game. Includes player turns, dice rolls, and win logic.

## Features

- Simulates multiple players
- Uses random dice rolls
- Win condition logic

## Technologies

- Python
- random module

## How to Run

```bash
python ludo.py
